OL,3,CGovernment to reconsider decision to
OL,4,Cdeny Waspi women compensation
OL,6,FThe government will reconsider the
OL,7,Fdecision not to award compensation to
OL,8,FWaspi women after new evidence
OL,9,Femerged, the Works and Pensions
OL,10,FSecretary said.
OL,12,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,13,FMcFadden said the government would
OL,14,Fretake the decision to deny
OL,15,Fcompensation to the women born in the
OL,16,F1950s, whose state pension age was
OL,17,Fraised so it would be equal with men.
