OL,3,CGovernment to reconsider decision to
OL,4,Cdeny Waspi women compensation
OL,6,FHe said it comes after "evidence"
OL,7,Fwhich was not shown to his predecessor
OL,8,FLiz Kendall when she made the decision
OL,9,Flast December had since come to light
OL,10,Fand needed to be considered.
OL,12,FThe decision to refuse compensation
OL,13,Fwas made despite a recommendation by
OL,14,Fthe Parliamentary and Health Service
OL,15,FOmbudsman (PHSO) the women should be
OL,16,Fpaid up to #2,950 each, a package with
OL,17,Fa potential total cost of #10.5
OL,18,Fbillion to the public purse, as poor
OL,19,Fcommunication meant they had lost out
OL,20,Fon the chance to plan their retirement
OL,21,Ffinances.
