OL,3,CGovernment to reconsider decision to
OL,4,Cdeny Waspi women compensation
OL,6,FMcFadden, however, suggested to MPs
OL,7,Fthat reconsidering the decision did
OL,8,Fnot mean the government would end up
OL,9,Fawarding the women compensation.
OL,11,FHe told the Commons: "Retaking this
OL,12,Fdecision should not be taken as an
OL,13,Findication that the government will
OL,14,Fnecessarily decide that it should
OL,15,Faward financial redress.
OL,17,F"The work will begin immediately and I
OL,18,Fwill update the House on the decision
OL,19,Fas soon as a conclusion is reached."
