OL,3,CGovernment to reconsider decision to
OL,4,Cdeny Waspi women compensation
OL,6,FSince 2015 Women Against State Pension
OL,7,FInequality (Waspi) have been
OL,8,Fadvocating for support for 1950s-born
OL,9,Fwomen who say they did not get
OL,10,Fadequate warnings about changes to the
OL,11,Fstate pension.
OL,13,FIn 1995, the government changed the
OL,14,Flaw to increase women's state pension
OL,15,Fage from 60 to 65, to equalise the age
OL,16,Fwith men. The change would be phased
OL,17,Fin from 2010 over ten years.
