OL,3,CGovernment to reconsider decision to
OL,4,Cdeny Waspi women compensation
OL,6,FAround 3.5 million women who were on
OL,7,Fthe cusp of retirement, or heading
OL,8,Ftowards it, were affected when the
OL,9,Fchanges to the state pension age came
OL,10,Finto effect, when it began to be
OL,11,Fphased in from 2010 for women born
OL,12,Fbetween 1950 and 1955.
OL,14,FThe campaign group is not against
OL,15,Fequalisation of the state pension age,
OL,16,Fbut rather disputes the way the
OL,17,Fgovernment implemented changes "with
OL,18,Finadequate or no notice".
